Paper: hep-th/9905040

Date: 1999-05-06

Title: Discontinuities on strings

Comments: 9 pages, LaTeX

Instead of the infinitesimal extrinsic and intrinsic perturbations onstrings, considered so far, we discuss the evolution and propagation offinite-amplitude perturbations. Those intrinsic perturbations may result inappearance of stable discontinuities similar to the shock waves.